CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780592748
OL,3,CMakerfield by-election: Declared
OL,4,Ccandidates and everything else you
OL,5,Cneed to know
OL,7,FIn the eight Makerfield wards that
OL,8,Fvoted in the local election, Reform
OL,9,Fsecured 50% of the vote while Labour
OL,10,Fgot 23%.
OL,12,FThe constituency's former MP stood
OL,13,Fdown to allow the Mayor of Greater
OL,14,FManchester Andy Burnham to stand for
OL,15,Fhis seat and return to Westminster.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/25
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780592748
OL,3,CMakerfield by-election: Declared
OL,4,Ccandidates and everything else you
OL,5,Cneed to know
OL,7,FJosh Simons said: "This was not an
OL,8,Feasy thing to do, and I wouldn't have
OL,9,Fdone it unless I really, really
OL,10,Fbelieved, at the end of the day, that
OL,11,Fthis was in the best interests of the
OL,12,FLabour Party, my community, and most
OL,13,Fimportantly, the country."
OL,15,FBut with other parties keen to block
OL,16,Fhis return, Mr Burnham faces a
OL,17,Fdifficult fight to win over the people
OL,18,Fof the Makerfield constituency.
OL,26,@oD@SOUuD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/25
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
