OL,3,CMakerfield by-election: Declared
OL,4,Ccandidates and everything else you
OL,5,Cneed to know
OL,7,FThe full list of candidates, in
OL,8,Falphabetical order, standing in the by-
OL,9,Felection, being held on 18 June are:
OL,11,FJake Austin (Lib Dem)
OL,13,FJake Austin has been announced as the
OL,14,FLiberal Democrat candidate.
OL,16,FHe was born and raised in Hindley, and
OL,17,Fhas lived in Greater Manchester his
OL,18,Fwhole life. Working in fundraising,
OL,19,FJake is also a Liberal Democrat
OL,20,FCouncillor.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/25
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780592748
OL,3,CMakerfield by-election: Declared
OL,4,Ccandidates and everything else you
OL,5,Cneed to know
OL,7,FHe'd also previously been a Liberal
OL,8,FDemocrat candidate in the Greater
OL,9,FManchester Mayorality election.
OL,11,FCommenting on his selection, Jake
OL,12,FAustin said:
OL,14,F"I'm thrilled to have been selected as
OL,15,Fthe Liberal Democrat candidate for
OL,16,FMakerfield. Voters in Makerfield
OL,17,Fdeserve so much more than the failing
OL,18,FLabour government or the divisive
OL,19,Fpolitics of Reform UK.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/25
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
