OL,3,CMakerfield by-election: Declared
OL,4,Ccandidates and everything else you
OL,5,Cneed to know
OL,7,FDescribing himself as a intergalactic
OL,8,Fspace warrior and leader of the
OL,9,FRecyclons from planet Sigma IX, Count
OL,10,FBinface is campaigning on the message
OL,11,Fof "Makerfield great again".
OL,13,FCount Binface won 24,260 votes in the
OL,14,FLondon Mayoral Election in 2024. Later
OL,15,Fthat year they took on Prime Minister
OL,16,FRishi Sunak at the General Election in
OL,17,FRichmond and Northallerton, winning
OL,18,F308 votes.
OL,20,FAndy Burnham (Labour)
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/25
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
