OL,4,Ccandidates and everything else you
OL,5,Cneed to know
OL,7,FHe is the party's co-ordinator for the
OL,8,FNorth-West and stood in the Gorton and
OL,9,FDenton by-election, also in Greater
OL,10,FManchester, in February.
OL,12,FEd Gemmell (Climate Party)
OL,14,FLeader of the Climate Party Ed Gemmell
OL,15,Fis standing in the Makerfield by-
OL,16,Felection.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/25
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
