OL,3,CMakerfield by-election: Declared
OL,4,Ccandidates and everything else you
OL,5,Cneed to know
OL,7,FGemmell believes that "none of the
OL,8,Fmainstream parties are capitalising on
OL,9,Fthis economic opportunity, which has
OL,10,Fled to the establishment of the
OL,11,FClimate Party - the only pro-business,
OL,12,Fpro-climate political party".
OL,14,FHe said "A vote for me is a vote for a
OL,15,Fricher, greener Britain."
OL,17,FRobert Kenyon (Reform UK)
OL,19,FMakerfield-born plumber and gas
OL,20,Fengineer Robert Kenyon is Reform UK's
OL,21,Fcandidate.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/25
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
