OL,3,CMakerfield by-election: Declared
OL,4,Ccandidates and everything else you
OL,5,Cneed to know
OL,7,FIn a campaign video, he claimed to be
OL,8,Fthe first MP born in Makerfield to
OL,9,Frepresent the constituency.
OL,11,FHe said: "It get's me a bit emotional
OL,12,Fsometimes, thinking that I could be
OL,13,Frepresenting people in Parliament.
OL,14,FIt's a massive honour. People are
OL,15,Fgoing to think: hang on, he serviced
OL,16,Fmy boiler last week.
OL,18,F"People in this area have been taken
OL,19,Fadvantage of for too long. The
OL,20,FMakerfield constituency deserves a
OL,21,Flocal champion."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/25
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
