OL,3,CMakerfield by-election: Declared
OL,4,Ccandidates and everything else you
OL,5,Cneed to know
OL,7,FKenyon stood in the constituency for
OL,8,FReform UK in the 2024 general
OL,9,Felection, where he came second to
OL,10,FLabour's Josh Simons.
OL,12,FAlan 'Howlin' Laud Hope (Monster
OL,13,FRaving Loony Party)
OL,15,FParty leader and co-founder Alan
OL,16,F'Howlin' Laud Hope is the candidate
OL,17,Ffor the Monster Raving Loony party.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/25
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
