OL,3,CMakerfield by-election: Declared
OL,4,Ccandidates and everything else you
OL,5,Cneed to know
OL,7,FIn a statement, the party said: "We
OL,8,Fcan confirm that our glorious leader
OL,9,FAlan 'Howlin' Laud Hope with selected
OL,10,Fagents will be standing against Andy
OL,11,FBurnham in the forthcoming election in
OL,12,FMakerfield.
OL,14,F"We can also confirm that there is no
OL,15,Fintention to launch a leadership bid
OL,16,Fto replace our leader."
OL,18,FHope founded the party alongside
OL,19,F'ScreamingLord Sutch' at a pub in
OL,20,FDevon in 1982.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/25
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
