OL,3,CMakerfield by-election: Declared
OL,4,Ccandidates and everything else you
OL,5,Cneed to know
OL,7,FHe previously stood in the Runcorn and
OL,8,FHelsby by-election, where he received
OL,9,F128 votes.
OL,11,FRebecca Shepherd (Restore Britain)
OL,13,FLocal businesswoman Rebecca Shepherd
OL,14,Fhas been announced as Restore
OL,15,FBritain's candidate.
OL,17,FA party statement said: "Rebecca has
OL,18,Fspent most of her adult life living
OL,19,Fand working in the Wigan borough,
OL,20,Fwhere she has built and run her own
OL,21,Fsmall business.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/25
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
