PN,39217
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780592748
OL,3,CMakerfield by-election: Declared
OL,4,Ccandidates and everything else you
OL,5,Cneed to know
OL,7,F"Through that experience, she
OL,8,Funderstands first-hand the pressures
OL,9,Ffacing local businesses and working
OL,10,Fpeople across the community."
OL,12,FRestore Britain, which was created by
OL,13,FGreat Yarmouth MP Rupert Lowe in
OL,14,FFebruary after he left Reform UK, said
OL,15,FRebecca Shepherd would prioritise
OL,16,Fimproving SEND access, creating safer
OL,17,Fstreets for women and girls, and
OL,18,F"fight reckless overdevelopment."
OL,20,FSarah Wakefield (Green Party)
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G17/25
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39218
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780592748
OL,3,CMakerfield by-election: Declared
OL,4,Ccandidates and everything else you
OL,5,Cneed to know
OL,7,FManchester City Councillor Sarah
OL,8,FWakefield has been selected as Green
OL,9,FParty candidate.
OL,11,FThe 38-year-old mum-of-two is
OL,12,Fcurrently on maternity leave as a
OL,13,Fcharity director, she previously
OL,14,Fworked in retail with a focus on
OL,15,Fsustainable food and is a trustee of a
OL,16,Fcommunity organisation.
OL,18,F"I am proud to be representing the
OL,19,FGreen Party in the Makerfield by-
OL,20,Felection," she said.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G18/25
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39219
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780592748
OL,3,CMakerfield by-election: Declared
OL,4,Ccandidates and everything else you
OL,5,Cneed to know
OL,7,F"It is vital in a democracy that
OL,8,Fvoters are given a choice of who they
OL,9,Fwant to vote for. Together we can
OL,10,Fbring back the hope that politics can
OL,11,Fcreate a better life for ourselves and
OL,12,Four children. This is what the Green
OL,13,FParty represents.
OL,15,F"We showed in Gorton and Denton we can
OL,16,Ftake on and beat Reform, whose
OL,17,Fbackward-looking and divisive politics
OL,18,Fneeds to be challenged head-on with a
OL,19,Fmessage that the future can be better
OL,20,Fand fairer than the failed status quo.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G19/25
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
