SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780592748
OL,3,CMakerfield by-election: Declared
OL,4,Ccandidates and everything else you
OL,5,Cneed to know
OL,7,F"Don't vote in anger, vote in hope."
OL,9,FPeter Ward (The Rejoin EU Party)
OL,11,FThe Rejoin EU Party announced
OL,12,Fbarrister Peter Ward will stand as its
OL,13,Fcandidate.
OL,15,FParty chairman Brendan Donnelly said:
OL,16,F"Rejoining the EU has come back into
OL,17,Fthe British political debate in a big
OL,18,Fway. The Rejoin EU Party intends to
OL,19,Fmake a full contribution to this
OL,20,Fdiscussion. That's why we're standing
OL,21,Fin Makerfield.
OL,26,@oD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G20/25
