CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780592748
OL,3,CMakerfield by-election: Declared
OL,4,Ccandidates and everything else you
OL,5,Cneed to know
OL,7,F"In addition to that, in recent months
OL,8,Fit's become increasingly clear that
OL,9,Four EU partners will want to be sure
OL,10,Fthat once returned to the EU, the UK
OL,11,Fwon't leave again at a later date."
OL,13,F"The Rejoin EU Party believes a new
OL,14,Fvoting system is necessary to
OL,15,Fguarantee future political stability
OL,16,Fin the UK.
OL,18,F"We'll therefore be stressing in our
OL,19,Fcampaign the need for the UK rapidly
OL,20,Fto move towards a system of
OL,21,Fproportional representation."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G21/25
