OL,3,CMakerfield by-election: Declared
OL,4,Ccandidates and everything else you
OL,5,Cneed to know
OL,7,FMichael Winstanley (Conservatives)
OL,9,FFormer Wigan councillor Michael
OL,10,FWinstanley has been selected as the
OL,11,FConservative Party candidate.
OL,13,FHe was born and lives in Makerfield,
OL,14,Fgrowing up above his parents' corner
OL,15,Fshop in Ashton-in-Makerfield.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G22/25
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
