OL,3,CMakerfield by-election: Declared
OL,4,Ccandidates and everything else you
OL,5,Cneed to know
OL,7,FWinstanley was selected as the
OL,8,FConservative candidate for the
OL,9,FMakerfield constituency in 1997 before
OL,10,Fserving as a Wigan councillor for
OL,11,FOrrell for 16 years, having first been
OL,12,Felected in 2000.
OL,14,FHe said: "Makerfield has always been
OL,15,Fat the heart of everything I do. I
OL,16,Fknow the pride people have in our
OL,17,Ftowns and villages, but I also
OL,18,Funderstand the challenges families and
OL,19,Fbusinesses are facing because of this
OL,20,FGovernment's decisions.
OL,26,@vD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G23/25
