OL,3,CMakerfield by-election: Declared
OL,4,Ccandidates and everything else you
OL,5,Cneed to know
OL,7,F"Under Kemi Badenoch, the Conservative
OL,8,FParty has changed and has clear plans
OL,9,Fto build Stronger High Streets and Get
OL,10,FBritain Working Again.
OL,12,F"This by-election is an opportunity to
OL,13,Fgive Makerfield a strong local voice
OL,14,Fwho understands the area and has a
OL,15,Fproven record of delivering for the
OL,16,Farea and I am looking forward to the
OL,17,Fcampaign."
OL,19,FIndependents
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@JO]
